      <h2>Selected Law Firms</h2>

        <p>Dr. Lavian is a technical expert in network <a href="/us-10348313-radar-target-detection-system/">communications</a>, <a href="/us-20180130102-reliable-rating-system-and-method-thereof/">telecommunications</a>, and Internet Protocols. He focuses on software development and implementation of various technology products. In addition to his technical expertise, he has extensive experience as an expert witness in legal cases involving patents and other intellectual property issues.</p>

        <p>Several prominent law firms have hired Dr. Lavian to provide expert witness testimony and consulting services, including Fish Richardson, Cooley, Oblon, Irell & Manella, McKool Smith, Keker Van Nest, Finnegan, Holland & Knight, Perkins Coie, Kirkland & Ellis, Desmarais, Morgan Lewis, Kenyon & Kenyon, Durie Tangri, Greenberg Traurig, Ropes & Gray, McGuireWoods, Paper Hamilton, Skadden, Winston & Strawn, Gibson Dunn, Simpson Thacher, and Foley & Lardner. These firms are known for their expertise in <a href="/us-20130080898-electronic-communications/">network communications</a>, telecommunications, and Internet Protocols and their reputation for providing high-quality legal services to their clients.</p>

        <p>Dr. Lavian has testified in various courts, including the United States District Court, the USPTO, the ITC, and other courts in the United States and Canada. He has also provided expert testimony in USPTO PTAB proceedings, including IPRs, CBM reviews, PGRs, Ex-Parte Re-Examinations, and PTO Interferences. His technical knowledge and expertise make him a valuable resource for these selected law firms.</p>

